ennsylvania in  mr jacobson was selected to serve as a member of our board because of his knowledge of finance and capital markets gained through his investment experience at highfields and other investment funds source iheartmedia inc on      sign up for equilar atlas and view jonathon s jacobsons full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like jonathon s jacobson more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in jonathon s jacobsons network and community follow changes in jonathon s jacobsons employment and moneyinmotion connect with jonathon s jacobson through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example jonathon s jacobson popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla daniel a dematteo executive chairman gamestop corp david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for your interest ok browse executive profiles  a  b  c  d  e  f  g  h  i  j  k  l  m  n  o  p  q  r  s  t  u  v  w  x  y  z equilar homepage equilar atlas equilar insight equilar boardedge equilar engage research services knowledge network about us login �  equilar all rights reserved privacy policy  marshall street redwood city ca   phone    fax   highfields capital highfields capital management lp founded by jonathon s jacobson in  is a valueoriented investment management firm which manages private investment funds for endowments charitable and philanthropic foundations pension funds and other institutional and private investors highfields investment funds have over  billion in assets under management invested worldwide in public and private companies across a wide variety of industries and security types the firm pursues a fundamental value investment approach as one team for one process in one office located in boston massachusetts for company managements and others  user name is required  password is required user id   password   investors for access to the highfields capital management investors’ website please go to hcmclientcom to request access please contact highfields capital at   or at highfields capital and its managed funds are not open for investment by members of the publicno offer of interests in such funds is being made or should be inferred   jonathon s jacobson  littlesis jonathon s jacobson highfields capital cofounder add relationship edit flag tweet edited by kevin  months ago history jonathon s jacobson founded highfields capital management lp in july  prior to founding highfields he spent eight years as a senior equity jonathon s jacobson founded highfields capital management lp in july  prior to founding highfields he spent eight years as a senior equity portfolio manager at harvard management company inc hmc which is responsible for investing harvard universitys endowment at hmc mr jacobson managed both a us and an emerging markets equity fund from  to  he was vice president in the equity arbitrage group at lehman brothers in new york where he managed a proprietary trading account focused on optionsoriented arbitrage strategies from  to  he was an investment banking analyst at merrill lynch capital markets in new york and sydney australia mr jacobson currently serves as a director of cc media holdings inc and is a member of the asset managers committee of the presidents working group on financial markets which was formed in  to foster a dialogue with the federal reserve board and department of the treasury on issues of significance to the investment industry mr jacobson is devoted to numerous philanthropic causes he is a trustee of brandeis university where he is a member of both the executive and investment committees and gilman school where he also serves on the investment committee he also serves on the boards of the birthright israel foundation and facing history and ourselves and is a member of the board of deans advisors at the harvard business school mr jacobson received an mba from harvard business school in  and graduated magna cum laude with a bs in economics from the wharton school university of pennsylvania in  more » « less relationships interlocks giving political data business positions highfields capital management hedge fund that manages portion of harvards endowment • cofounder jul → lehman brothers th largest investment bank in the usa before  bankruptcy • vice president in the equity arbitrage group → merrill lynch the wealth management brokerage and investment banking arm of bank of america • analyst → iheartcommunications inc a diversified media company • board member aug → other positions harvard management company inc manages much of harvards endowment • senior equity portfolio manager → brandeis university a jewishsponsored secular university near boston • trustee gilman school elite school in baltimore md • trustee education harvard business school • graduate → university of pennsylvania wharton school penn business school • undergraduate → holdings iheartcommunications inc a diversified media company • major shareholder aug → donationgrant recipients showing  of   see all security is strength •  contribution ·  jun   independent voice for illinois •  contribution ·  mar   america leads chris christie aligned super pac •  contribution ·  jan   national republican senatorial committee •  contributions ·  → emergency committee for israel pac •  contribution ·   mark steven kirk us senator and representative from illinois •  contributions ·  →apr   kirk victory cmte •  contribution ·  apr   mitt romney former governor of massachusetts •  contributions ·  →jun   