llery   homeabout usdr jonathan s jacobs dr jacobs received a degree from the university of rochester in  and attended harvard school of dental medicine where he graduated cum laude in  from  through  he studied at vanderbilt university completing a combined residency in oral and maxillofacial surgery and general surgery he remained at vanderbilt as the acting chairman of the department of oral  maxillofacial surgery until  when he moved to virginia beach to complete a residency in plastic and reconstructive surgery at the eastern virginia graduate school of medicine dr jacobs has been practicing plastic surgery in the hampton roads area for the last  years and has been on the faculty of our medical school that entire time locally he has volunteered as an interviewer for candidates for admission to eastern virginia medical school and was chairman of the surgical executive committee at sentara leigh hospital for seven years currently the associate professor of clinical plastic surgery at evms dr jacobs has contributed substantially to medical literature by publishing  scientific papers and book chapters he is an alumni interviewer for students wishing admission to vanderbilt university as a very active member of state and national plastic surgical organizations dr jacobs was past president of both the american society of maxillofacial surgeons and the virginia society of plastic and reconstructive surgeons he served as membership chairman of the american society of temporomandibular joint surgeons additionally as a member of the american society of plastic and reconstructive surgeons the largest group of plastic surgeons in the world he served in board of directors and was the chairman of the ethics committee boardcertified in both plastic and reconstructive surgery and oral and maxillofacial surgery dr jacobs has acted as a guest examiner for the american board of plastic surgeons his current interests are in cosmetic and breast surgery and he brings special expertise to associates in plastic surgery in regard to maxillofacial surgery on his annual visits to honduras dr jacobs is senior surgeon for the world pediatric project and has volunteered his surgical care and teaching in third world countries on more than twenty such trips dr jacobs was selected as the top plastic surgeon in virginia beach by the international association of healthcare professionals read full coverage here dr jacobs was has also been listed as one of americas top breast surgeons of  see more here     patient testimonials written testimonials  board certified plastic surgeons face breast body medspa in the press our doctors at associates in plastic surgery have appeared in a fourpage ad in new beauty magazine which highlighted our wide array of breast enhancement body contouring and facial rejuvenation procedures read more restoration medspa injectables lasers skincare products coolsculpting schedule a consultation first namelast nameemailphoneprocedure of interestprocedure of interestarm liftbody contouring after massive weight lossbody liftbotoxbreast augmentationbreast liftbreast reconstructionbreast reductionbrow liftbuttocks enhancementcoolsculptingeyelid surgeryfaceliftfacial implantsfacials  peelsfat graftinginjectable fillersintense pulsed lightkybellalatisselip augmentationliposuctionmini faceliftmommy makeoverneckliftotoplastyrhinoplastyskincare productsthigh lifttummy tuckotherdoctordoctordr alspaughdr denkdr jacobsmedspainjectablespatient typenew patientexisting patientcommentscaptcha locate our offices   virginia beach office  first colonial road virginia beach va  phone   norfolk office  kempsville road suite  norfolk va  phone   surgery center breast augmentation tummy tuck medspa gallery copyright   associates in plastic surgery  site map plastic surgery marketing and website design by vba dr jacobs board certified plastic surgeon in virginia beach norfolk va vba virginia beach office first colonial roadvirginia beachva  norfolk office k